Note: Only basic attacks can critically strike (not boosted attacks), but Mew has 0% base Critical-Hit rate at all levels. At level 9, Mew gains 12.5% spell vamp (restores HP when dealing Special Attack damage).

Synchronize

Passive Ability

Each time Mew uses a move, Mew and nearby allies have their movement speed increased by 15% for 2s.

Move Reset

Passive Ability

When Mew reaches level 5, the Move Reset icon can be used to reset Mew's moves and learn new moves. This ability goes on a 25s cooldown after it's used. Each time Mew knocks out or makes an assist on an enemy player, or scores a goal, the Move Reset cooldown is reduced (Knockout: 40%, Assist: 20%, Goal: 5%). Using Move Reset adds 5000 Unite Move energy to Mystical Mirage.

Attack

Auto Attack

Each time Mew uses a move, they gain a boost counter. A maximum of 3 boost counters can be stored. After 3 counters are stored (they have to be consumed within 8s or they disappear), Mew's next basic attack becomes a boosted attack that consumes all counters and launches a ball of psychic energy at an enemy. During the lock-on animation Mew can use moves. The further the ball travels, the more damage it deals (4% more damage per threshold, stacking additively). This ball pierces through wild Pokémon, but will stop traveling upon contact with the first enemy player.

100% Atk + 0 x (Level - 1) + 0

160% SpA + 8 x (Level - 1) + 280

Electro Ball

Move 1 Option

5.00s Sure Hit

Hurl an electric orb, dealing damage to enemies in the area-of-effect and leaving them paralyzed (40% slow) for 2s. This move deals more damage the lower the enemies' remaining HP is.

Through Light Screen: Damage dealt and area-of-effect radius are increased.

109% SpA + 11 x (Level - 1) + 250

141.7% SpA + 14 x (Level - 1) + 325

Strengthens the effect of the paralysis inflicted by this move to 60%.

Solar Beam

Move 1 Option

9.00s Area

Blast a bundled beam of light, dealing damage 3 times to enemies in the area-of-effect. If this move hits an enemy, Mew gains an additional boost counter.

Through Light Screen: Damage dealt and area-of-effect radius are increased.

58% SpA + 3 x (Level - 1) + 120

75% SpA + 4 x (Level - 1) + 156

Reduce this move's cooldown by 0.5s for each enemy hit.

Surf

Move 1 Option

12.00s Hindrance

Charge forward on a wave, shoving enemies for 0.5s and leaving them unable to act for 0.5s. Mew gains a shield for 3s and becomes immune to hindrances while using this move. At the end of this move, Mew can jump in a designated direction and becomes immune to hindrances for a short time. If this move hits an enemy, Mew gains an additional boost counter.

Through Light Screen: Distance the wave travels is increased and Light Screen attaches to Mew.

185% SpA + 7 x (Level - 1) + 320

70% SpA + 0 x (Level - 1) + 200

Strengthens the shield effect of this move.

100% SpA + 0 x (Level - 1) + 300

Coaching

Move 2 Option

7.00s Buff

Teleport to an ally, granting them a shield for 3s and increasing basic attack speed by 40% for 2s. If this move is used on an ally who hasn't been coached within 7s, the cooldown of this move is reduced by 90%. If this move is used on an ally who has been recently coached, this move goes on cooldown. The cooldown of Electro Ball, Solar Beam, and Surf is reduced by 1s each time this move is used.

100% SpA + 0 x (Level - 1) + 300

Reduce this move's cooldown by 1s and reduces the timer of recently coached on allies to 6s.

Light Screen

Move 2 Option

9.00s Buff

Create a translucent wall in the designated location for 4s that prevents enemies from passing and shoves them for 0.5s if they make contact with the wall. If Mew's Electro Ball, Solar Beam, or Surf passes through the wall, the effects of those moves will be enhanced (such as increased damage, range, and area-of-effect). If this move is used again within 4s, the wall is pulled towards Mew and follows them as they move for an additional 4s. While the wall moves with Mew, enemy attacks that pass through it will deal 25% reduced damage but will not prevent enemies from passing and does not shove them anymore.

Increases the size of the wall.

Agility

Move 2 Option

10.00s Dash

Move quickly in a designated direction, increasing Mew's movement speed by 5% for 2s. Holds 2 uses in reserve and cannot be used more than once every 2s.

Increases the distance Mew moves in the designated direction.

Mystical Mirage

Unite Move

123s 110000 Area

Unlocks at level 8

Mew becomes unstoppable and floats in the air for 1s, then becoming invincible and invisible for up to 6s until using an attack or move. A field is created around Mew for 5s This field travels with Mew. Mew and all allies within the area become stealthed for 4s. After the field expires, this move deals damage to enemies within the area-of-effect.

120% SpA + 10 x (Level - 1) + 340

Unite Buffs (6s duration):

30% Movement Speed, 30% CDR, 20% Max HP Shield
